  "detailed_description": "This is a military-themed single-player shooting game produced by individual developers. In the game, you will play the role of a commander, drive a tank and command your companions, search for and assassinate the enemy's field commander in the wilderness.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Forming A Team</h2>As a commander, you can configure your armored units in the garage<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/4bba90e4bbf8e07fffb3c98e8891e482.poster.avif?t=1694865846\" width=478 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/4bba90e4bbf8e07fffb3c98e8891e482.webm?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/4bba90e4bbf8e07fffb3c98e8891e482.mp4?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Charging</h2>You need drive the currently selected equipment with the keyboard and mouse.<br>As a commander, you can give orders to your partner vehicle, mark the march or fire the target<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/7a290ca1b855fcd3252fba0de65e0ec7.poster.avif?t=1694865846\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/7a290ca1b855fcd3252fba0de65e0ec7.webm?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/7a290ca1b855fcd3252fba0de65e0ec7.mp4?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Covert Assassination</h2>The battlefield is full of enemy scouts, don't be spotted by them, otherwise more armored troops will come to support.<br>Long-distance covert assassination is a good option<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/b58f253ec9095ededd43aef87b361622.poster.avif?t=1694865846\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/b58f253ec9095ededd43aef87b361622.webm?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/b58f253ec9095ededd43aef87b361622.mp4?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reconnaissance and Beyond Visual Range Strike</h2>A good commander will reasonably allocate the roles of the convoy<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Helicopters and wheeled vehicles have powerful maneuverability to penetrate behind enemy lines and discover key targets.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/7973626596121fff45536a22ed57226e.poster.avif?t=1694865846\" width=478 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/7973626596121fff45536a22ed57226e.webm?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/7973626596121fff45536a22ed57226e.mp4?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Mark targets and conduct long-range precision strikes<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/bc9b07fcdeb0b02edb7b30c97f78dcae.poster.avif?t=1694865846\" width=478 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/bc9b07fcdeb0b02edb7b30c97f78dcae.webm?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/bc9b07fcdeb0b02edb7b30c97f78dcae.mp4?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be Careful</h2>The enemy is ambushing some key roads by surprise, so be careful！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/1887e0615ab439dbcb00e6454701463d.poster.avif?t=1694865846\" width=478 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/1887e0615ab439dbcb00e6454701463d.webm?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304570/extras/1887e0615ab439dbcb00e6454701463d.mp4?t=1694865846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Terminate The Invader[/h2]<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Breakthrough the enemy armored force line, search and destroy the command post of the invaders！！</li></ul>",
